definitions.definition: A market town and civil parish with a town council in Cheshire West and Chester , Cheshire , England ( OS grid ref SJ6566 ) .
A small village and civil parish in Somerset , England , previously in Somerset West and Taunton district ( OS grid ref SS9034 ) .
